      <title>马斯克未能将选民抽奖案件提交美国法院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/musk-loses-bid-to-send-philadelphia-sweepstakes-case-to-us-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）未能将一项针对他每天向选民赠送百万美元的奖金的诉讼移交联邦法院，而这起诉讼由费城进步派地方检察官提起，并再次交由州法院法官审理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/musk-loses-bid-to-send-philadelphia-sweepstakes-case-to-us-court</guid>
